OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight mist or fog
OL,6,Flifting through the morning. Staying
OL,7,Fdry but much cooler with variable
OL,8,Fcloud in the east. Still warm with
OL,9,Fprolonged spells of sunshine in the
OL,10,Fwest, light winds here too.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry evening with plenty of
OL,13,Fsunshine to enjoy, perhaps still
OL,14,Fcloudy around East Lothian. Cloud
OL,15,Ffilling in during the night with some
OL,16,Flight rain around the west by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
