OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy with some light showers
OL,6,Fin place, some brighter spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping later in the day for
OL,8,FDumfries and Galloway, winds remaining
OL,9,Flight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA
OL,12,Fbright start on Monday but a few
OL,13,Fshowers developing and cloudy at
OL,14,Ftimes. Remaining settled on Tuesday
OL,15,Fand Wednesday with bright or sunny
OL,16,Fspells and light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
